Body: I once installed a game called traffic racer on my nokia x2. It ran very well on the first day and it won't run again. I did not update the game or my phone or changed anything. Did a complete reset of my phone. Even tried formatting the device and rooting and what not. Still no luck ! Is the same happening with any of you ? How to solve this ?
